  "detailed_description": "Just stop and relax. Forget about all the fuss and feel the magic of music in this game. <br />\r\nFour different modes: <br />\r\n1. Logic arcade in style \"3 in row\"<br />\r\n2. Classical puzzle game, where you need assembly the image from pieces, <br />\r\n3. Arcade in \"bubble shooter\" style, where you need to shoot at groups of gems with the same color. <br />\r\n4. Memory game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures: <br />\r\n5 different scenes<br />\r\n4 game modes<br />\r\n26 images for puzzle mode + support of custom images<br />\r\n12 music tracks with different mood<br />\r\nRandomization of ambient and decorations",
  "about_the_game": "Just stop and relax. Forget about all the fuss and feel the magic of music in this game. <br />\r\nFour different modes: <br />\r\n1. Logic arcade in style \"3 in row\"<br />\r\n2. Classical puzzle game, where you need assembly the image from pieces, <br />\r\n3. Arcade in \"bubble shooter\" style, where you need to shoot at groups of gems with the same color. <br />\r\n4. Memory game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures: <br />\r\n5 different scenes<br />\r\n4 game modes<br />\r\n26 images for puzzle mode + support of custom images<br />\r\n12 music tracks with different mood<br />\r\nRandomization of ambient and decorations",
